spur
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a ridge or side hill; in NZ one would probably `go up a spur to get on to a (main) ridge'
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
